====== Installing OTAWA ======

===== Dependencies =====

Tools:
  * Bison
  * CMake
  * Flex
  * G++
  * LibXML2
  * LibXSLT

Optional tool:
  * Doxygen
  * GraphViz
  * Thot

Internal dependencies (that must be compiled at the same level than OTAWA directory):
  * GEL
  * ELM (compiled with XOM extension)

Optional dependencies:
  * ppc2 (with gliss2)
  * armv5t (with gliss2)
  * lp_solve


===== Installation ======

To configure the make file, type:
<code sh>
cmake . -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=path_to_install_to
</code>

To compile OTAWA, just:
<code sh>
make all
</code>

To install it:
<code sh>
make install
</code>
